Description
This is a metabolism reconstruction of Staphylococcus haemolyticus JCSC1435Version: 1.02 on average european diet
Authors: Stefania Magnusdottir, Almut Heinken, Laura Kutt, Dmitry A. Ravcheev, Eugen Bauer, Alberto Noronha, Kacy Greenhalgh, Christian Jaeger, Joanna Baginska, Paul Wilmes, Ronan M.T. Fleming, and Ines Thiele.
